[4] Angola (Uige)
Date: Wed 26 Jun 2013
Source: Angop, Angola Press [In French, trans., edited]
http://www.portalangop.co.ao/motix/fr_fr/noticias/saude/2013/5/26/moins-nouveaux-cas-rougeole-notifies-Uige,643f0885-925a-489e-afc5-fab8b7861cc3.html


A total of 45 new cases of measles were registered between 17 and 23 Jun 2013 in Uige, according to the Angop news agency on 26 Jun 2013. According to a reliable source, these new cases were registered in the municipalities of Uige, Negage, Quimbele, Sanza Pombo, Songo, Ambuila, Buengas, Bungo Milunga and Maquela do Zombo. This source further stated that the municipality Uige is the worst affected with 9 cases.

--
